ovide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f683b80b-5724-4089-8452-4165774a9cf0","uuid":"cc5537c7-86f6-4ea3-9d1b-a39d930ff2df","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:58:23.456Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizm-docs/changelog.prizm","content":"MODULE: changelog\nRESPONSIBILITY: Append-only record of prizm-docs structural changes\n\nCHANGELOG:\n- 2026-03-23 | root.prizm | add: initial L0 doc; rules for F-024/F-025/F-026/F-027/F-028/F-029/F-030/F-031/F-032\n- 2026-03-23 | src/services.prizm | update: profile-store.js, backendRegistry.updateBackend() interfaces + TRAPS (F-021)\n- 2026-03-23 | src/bot.prizm | update: cli.js KEY_FILES, profile-store/backend-registry DEPENDENCIES (F-021)\n- 2026-03-23 | public/ | add: F-033 toast, F-034 spinner, F-035 kbd hints, F-036 empty state, F-037 scroll btn, F-038 copy btn\n- 2026-03-23 | root.prizm | update: RULES for toast/spinner/kbd/empty-state/scroll-btn/copy-btn (F-033–F-038)\n- 2026-03-23 | public/ | add: F-039 session info panel (.info-grid/.info-row + updateSessionInfoPanel JS)\n- 2026-03-23 | CLAUDE.md | update: sediment F-039 DECISIONS\n- 2026-03-23 | public/ | update: F-040 collapsible config panel (<details>/<summary> + arrow CSS)\n- 2026-03-23 | root.prizm | update: add collapsible config panel RULE (F-040)\n- 2026-03-23 | CLAUDE.md | update: sediment F-040 DECISIONS\n- 2026-03-23 | public/ | add: F-041 message timestamp (formatTimestamp, .message-timestamp, .message flex layout)\n- 2026-03-23 | root.prizm | update: add message timestamp RULE (F-041)\n- 2026-03-23 | CLAUDE.md | update: sediment F-041 DECISIONS\n- 2026-03-23 | public/ | add: F-043 font size toggle (--font-scale CSS var, .font-toggle CSS, applyFontSize/loadFontSize/setFontSize JS, 小/中/大 bu